title: All Right Now-The Sweet Featuring Ritchie Blackmore (Santa Monic
description:
All Right Now-The Sweet Featuring Ritchie Blackmore (Santa Monica Civic Center 24 March 1976)
Taken from Rainbow-Time standing Still (Bootleg)
Mp3 256 kbit/s
During an appearance at Santa Monica Civic Center Los Angeles, CA on 24 March 1976, Sweet played the Free classic "All Right Now" with Ritchie Blackmore as a tribute to mark the death of Free guitarist Paul Kossoff who died the week before from drug-related heart problems at the age of 25.
